title: Viper Challenge King of Mountain 2025

# Viper Challenge King of Mountain 2025

**Experience the ultimate obstacle race through Sunway's challenging terrain!**

## What to expect:
- 📍 Multiple challenging obstacles
- 💪 Test your physical and mental endurance
- 🏆 Compete for amazing prizes
- 🤝 Team-building opportunity

> "The toughest obstacle race in Malaysia" - *Fitness Malaysia*

[Register now](#) to secure your spot in this adrenaline-pumping event!

**Note:** Participants should arrive 30 minutes before the start time for briefing.
